VALUES ('ee316c41-7e63-4edb-98db-fa7ed55651f1', 'The student wants to trace the path from Fleming''s observation to wartime availability. Which choice most effectively uses relevant information from the notes to accomplish this goal?', 'Alexander Fleming and Penicillin
