VALUES ('985f21e3-ef66-4615-9ff5-b2adfc558104', 'The student wants to introduce the movement''s artistic aims and internal tensions. Which choice most effectively uses relevant information from the notes to accomplish this goal?', '• Writers and artists centered Black urban experience in 1920s Harlem.
