VALUES ('cb6cc84d-1b08-4c4d-a06e-253d4e8314e7', 'The student wants to explain how later evidence overcame initial skepticism. Which choice most effectively uses relevant information from the notes to accomplish this goal?', '• Alfred Wegener proposed continental drift in 1912.
