VALUES ('d4ff8aa0-8906-482c-849c-e65e456f059c', 'The student wants to emphasize how the movement challenged academic conventions. Which choice most effectively uses relevant information from the notes to accomplish this goal?', '• Parisian painters exhibited independently after Salon rejections in 1874.
