VALUES ('80d91458-fa3b-413a-a32d-7ec05ad90de1', 'The student wants to present humanitarian goals alongside strategic and economic dimensions. Which choice most effectively uses relevant information from the notes to accomplish this goal?', '• The United States pledged billions for European reconstruction after World War II.
