VALUES ('647f37cd-2a2c-48d6-9c76-3a988823b592', 'The student wants to explain how the architectural design of Tikal''s reservoir system directly addressed an environmental challenge of the region. Which choice most effectively uses relevant information from the notes to accomplish this goal?', 'Tikal''s Water Supply
